    <string name="advanced_protection_description">This device has Android\'s Advanced Protection turned on, which blocks all third-party accessibility services. TapLock relies on an accessibility service to lock the screen, so it can\'t work while Advanced Protection is enabled. To use TapLock, turn off Advanced Protection in Settings &gt; Security &amp; privacy.</string>
